<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>demo4amflow</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f6f7fb; }
      .wrap { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 24px; }
      .card { width: 100%; max-width: 520px; background: white; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); text-align: center; }
      h1 { margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 22px; }
      p { margin: 0 0 18px; color: #6b7280; }
      a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
      button { width: 100%; padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 14px; border: 1px solid #111827; background: #111827; color: white; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; }
      button:hover { opacity: 0.92; }
      .links { margin-top: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .links a { color: #2563eb; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="card">
        <h1>demo4amflow</h1>
        <p>点击按钮后将跳转到飞书登录并授权。</p>
        <a href="/consult"><button type="button">点击咨询</button></a>
        <div class="links">
          <a href="/chat">聊天</a>
          <a href="/idp/info">IdP 面板</a>
          <a href="/idp/requests">请求记录</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

